   Description:
                UFOS is a space combat game for two players. It's not 
                very new idea or great game but it sure is classic.
                It's challenging game for people whose age is between 5-99 
                years(eh..). UFOS is tested on A500 and on A1200.
                It's made in FINLAND(The ice-hockey champion 1995).

   Instructions:
                Player one(red):  Joystick up:      Move up
                                  Joystick Down:    Move down
                                  Joystick button:  Fire laser

                Player two(blue): Cursor up:        Move up
                                  Cursor down:      Move down
                                  Return:           Fire laser

                                  ESC:              Quit game(on battle)



